00:02:57.302 --> 00:02:58.613
Tunggu sebentar.

00:02:58.638 --> 00:02:59.873
Disini sangat dingin.

00:02:59.998 --> 00:03:01.764
Jangan khawatir sama sekali.

00:03:10.982 --> 00:03:12.091
Keluarkan aku!

00:03:12.154 --> 00:03:13.724
Tolong tetap kuat, kumohon!

00:03:26.052 --> 00:03:27.373
Ya Tuhan!

00:03:58.638 --> 00:03:59.708
Terima kasih.

00:04:17.025 --> 00:04:18.087
Itu terlalu bagus.

